These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: banana, papaya, grapes, corn, onion, pear, plum
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, thai, chinese, argentine, australian, british, italian
 1. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating corn is not the british##6
 3. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the italian is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
 5. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
 6. the pakistani is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the thai##7
 8. the thai is on the left of the italian##1
 9. the argentine is somewhere between the person eating onion and the chinese##7
10. the chinese is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
11. the australian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
13. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
14. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
15. the person eating onion is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | grapes    | banana    | papaya | pear | corn | onion    | plum |
| Nationality   | australian | pakistani | chinese  | british   | argentine    | thai | italian |

