.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, broccoli, carrot, cauliflower, plum, avocado, cranberry
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, drawing, card-games, traveling, writing, woodworking
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person eating cranberry and the person eating broccoli##7
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating cauliflower##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
 6. the person eating avocado is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 7. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating broccoli##7
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
10. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
11. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person eating cranberry##6
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person eating cauliflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | cranberry  | carrot | avocado | cauliflower | pear     | plum | broccoli  |
| Hobby   | drawing | writing | magic-tricks  | woodworking  | traveling | card-games      | photography |

