 3. the fan of salsa is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
 4. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 5. the fan of pop is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is photography##2
 6. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the fan of electronic##7
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
11. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is photography is not the fan of pop##6
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is photography##7
14. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
15. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
16. the person who's hobby is photography is not the fan of dubstep##6
17. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
18. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
19. the fan of pop is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
