 6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the tram##7
 8. the person who's sport is caring is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is rowing##7
12. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
13. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
