10. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
13. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person driving the car##7
14. the person who's sport is soccer is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is rowing##1
16. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
17. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
18. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

